Package: graphs
Type: Package
Title: Implements samplers for simple graphs conditional on vertex level data.
Version: 1.0
Date: 2017-12-02
Author@R: c(
	person("Scott", "James", email="james.scott15@imperial.ac.uk", role = c("aut","cre")),
	person("Gandy", "Axel", email = "a.gandy@imperial.ac.uk", role = "aut"))
Description: This package provides an efficient object oriented implementation of novel MCMC methods for sampling random graphs uniformly conditional on observed vertex degrees, and a specified set of arcs/edges. These techniques find application in motif detection and hypothesis testing. 
License: MIT
Imports: 
	methods, 
	Rcpp (>= 0.12.14)
LinkingTo: 
	Rcpp,
	testthat
Suggests: 
	testthat
